000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'',''),(8160,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/5 Burma soldiers in trenches and bunker with machine gun_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:48:45','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8161,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Arakan Dance_400.jpg','idx1','page','description','','','','Karen State, Burma: The tarp hangs loosely, strung up \r\nbetween two crooked goalposts. On it is a hand-drawn \r\nmap of Burma. Some 300 children sit on the ground, \r\nlooking at this map of their country. At least, we tell \r\nthem it is their country – they know it as Burma, while \r\ntheir country is “Kawthoolei” and both are distinct \r\nnations.','','','2013-02-12 16:49:08','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'',''),(8162,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Arakan Dance_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:49:08','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8163,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Arakan Surviving Children at IDP Camp_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:49:36','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8164,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/ASSK_400.jpg','idx1','page','description','','','','On 2 May 2012, Aung San Suu Kyi was sworn into Parliament in a historic session in \r\nwhich the long-time opposition leader and political prisoner officially became part of \r\nthe democratic process for which she has fought for so long. Her decision to contest the \r\nelections at the lower level of Parliament denoted her acceptance of the process towards \r\npeace being implemented by the current central government - though there is still \r\nwidespread uncertainty and speculation about President Thein Sein’s motives and ability \r\nto implement true democracy.','','','2013-02-12 16:50:38','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'',''),(8165,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Burma Army Gas munitions canister_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:51:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8166,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/burned tdd church with school_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:52:48','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8167,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/CIBglc (4)_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:54:46','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8168,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/CIBGLC dinner (2) - Copy_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:55:06','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8169,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/CIBhsa kae_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:56:08','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8170,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/CIBrun for relief in burned village.jupg_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:56:37','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8171,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/context7_400.jpg','idx1','page','description','','','','Many families live on very basic foods: rice, \r\nvegetables, chilies and salt. On special occasions \r\nthey may have meat. Decide with your family \r\nto prepare and eat a ‘meal of prayer’ for ethnic \r\npeople in Burma.','','','2013-02-12 16:57:06','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'',''),(8172,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/context7_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:57:06','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8173,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Copy of Sha gives thanks crop_400.jpg','idx1','page','description','','','','“Sha” was 8 years old and on her way to school when mushrooms caught her eye. \r\nAs she stepped off of the path to pick some, the landmine exploded and her life \r\nwas forever changed. Sha lost her right leg almost to her hip. That was nearly nine \r\nyears ago and she has grown from a little girl to a young woman, unable to run \r\nand play with others.','','','2013-02-12 16:57:45','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'',''),(8174,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Copy of Sha gives thanks crop_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:57:53','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','CCB'),(8175,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/cross silhouette dark people_400.jpg','idx1','page','description','','','','On 3 July 2012, Kyar Shell, Lahu relief team leader, \r\ndied of liver failure while on a mission. He leaves \r\nbehind his wife and young son. On 28 March 2012, Saw Kler Lay was killed by a \r\nlightning strike during a heavy thunderstorm. He was \r\nworking inside Burma in his home area of Karen State. On 6 March 2012, eight months into a long-range \r\nrelief mission, Hsaw Reh drowned while crossing the \r\nPon River in central Karenni State. He had been on \r\nhis way to pick up a supply of medicine so his team \r\ncould continue their mission.','','','2013-02-12 16:58:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'',''),(8176,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/cross silhouette dark people_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:58:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8177,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/DOP pneumonia baby_400.jpg','idx1','page','description','','','','So often, when we have given the best \r\nwe have, it still is not enough. But God sees, and comes alongside us, and \r\nbrings His own hand of healing into our little hospital and the lives of our \r\npatients. And for that we are grateful. --Dr. Kaw, \r\nTeacher at Jungle School of Medicine -- Kawthoolei','','','2013-02-12 16:59:03','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'',''),(8178,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/DOP pneumonia baby_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:59:03','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8179,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/DSC_0061_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:59:17','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8180,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/DSC_0138_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:59:32','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8181,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/DSC_0203_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 16:59:47','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8182,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/DSC_0226_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:00:03','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8183,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/During treatment boy at lotharawn village. he have stomach ache._400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:00:18','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8184,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/glc good luthaw (5)_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:00:37','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8185,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Hsaw Rey (4)_400.jpg','idx1','page','description','','','','On 6 March 2012, eight months into a long-range \r\nrelief mission, Hsaw Reh drowned while crossing the \r\nPon River in central Karenni State. He had been on \r\nhis way to pick up a supply of medicine so his team \r\ncould continue their mission. Hsaw Reh was 23. We \r\nare saddened by his death and extend our love and \r\nsorrow to his family, his team and his people. His \r\nloss will be greatly felt not just by all of us but also \r\nby those people he served so faithfully. To Hsaw Reh \r\nwe want to say, “Thank you and we thank God for \r\nyou. You were a good teammate and you served your \r\npeople well – you are an honor to your family, your \r\nteam and your people and we are blessed to have \r\nknown you.','','','2013-02-12 17:01:01','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'',''),(8186,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Hsaw Rey (4)_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:01:01','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8187,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/IDP interior - 2010-07-20 at 14-36-00BW_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:01:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8188,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/kachin grad photo_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:02:13','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8189,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Karennni_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:02:29','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8190,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Kler lay_400.jpg','idx1','page','description','','','','On 28 March 2012, Saw Kler Lay was killed by a \r\nlightning strike during a heavy thunderstorm. He was \r\nworking inside Burma in his home area of Karen State. \r\nKler Lay was a video cameraman as well as a deputy \r\nteam leader, and he had been serving his people on a \r\nrelief team since 2008. He was tough, smart and kind, \r\nand always willing to help and encourage others. He \r\nset an example of love, service, perseverance and \r\nprofessionalism that reflects great credit on him, \r\nhis people, the FBR and the KNU.','','','2013-02-12 17:02:51','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'',''),(8191,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Kler lay_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:02:51','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8192,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Kyar shell GLCBW_400.jpg','idx1','page','description','','','','On 3 July 2012, Kyar Shell, Lahu relief team leader, \r\ndied of liver failure while on a mission. He leaves \r\nbehind his wife and young son. He is loved and will \r\nbe missed by his family, his team and the people he \r\ndied serving. He was trained in 2004 and served with \r\ngreat dedication until his death. Kyar Shell was a \r\npioneering team leader, leading the first Lahu team in \r\na challenging and dangerous area of Shan State. His \r\nefforts resulted in saved lives and needed relief for \r\nthousands of Lahu and Shan people. He was a calm, \r\nhumble man with keen insight and compassion and \r\na man of action who took great risks to help people \r\nin need and never sought fame or glory.','','','2013-02-12 17:03:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'',''),(8193,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Kyar shell GLCBW_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:03:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8194,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/Mon team giving med care_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:03:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8195,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/P1160679_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:03:45','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8196,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/P1160810_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:03:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8197,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/P1160915_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:04:14','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8198,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/P1170144_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:04:29','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8199,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_Prayer/2013/images/SlideShow/400/P1170242_400.jpg','idx1','page','source','','','','','','','2013-02-12 17:04:42','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,1,'','FBR'),(8200,'/IDX/Prayer/Day_of_P